        <h5 class="title-certificate">
            1. SPECIAL EXERCISE PROGRAM OJT
        </h5>
        <p>
            OJT (On the job training) is a special business program of Greenwich University for 3rd year students. Designed with a duration of 4 months with 2 training periods, OJT gives students real knowledge. Currently, is an opportunity to help students experience their career, accumulate work experience and career after graduation.
        </p>
        <h5 class="title-certificate">
            2. EMPLOYMENT OPPORTUNITIES OPEN AFTER GRADUATION
        </h5>
        <p>
            Graduates of Greenwich University are welcome to work at FPT Corporation (with 7 member companies and more than 20,000 staff members), and hundreds of enterprises, partner groups in Vietnam as well as around the world
        </p>
        <h5 class="title-certificate">
            3. INTERNATIONAL ENVIRONMENT - STUDY WITH INTERNATIONAL TEACHERS AND STUDENTS
        </h5>
        <p>
            Greenwich University always tries to provide students with a comprehensive educational environment, bringing the values of professionalism. Students studying at the University of Greenwich will study in an environment similar to studying abroad with international curriculum, faculty and students from many countries around the world.
        </p>
        <h5 class="title-certificate">
            4. OPPORTUNITIES TO LEARN ABROAD
        </h5>
        <p>
            While studying at the school, Greenwich University students have the opportunity to experience the learning environment in countries outside Vietnam through student exchange programs, internships, seminars ... typically:

        <p> • English study program in the Philippines, Malaysia, Singapore ... </p>

        <p>
            • Experience indigenous life and cultural exchanges in other countries

        </p>
        <h5 class="title-certificate">5. COMPLETE YOURSELF WITH THE SKILL DEVELOPMENT PROGRAM (PDP) CHAIN</h5>
        <p>
            In addition to knowledge, students will be comprehensively developed with life skills training, soft skills through skill classes and many exciting experiential activities.
        </p>
        <h5 class="title-certificate">6. Cost is equal to 1/10 compared to studying abroad in the UK</h5>
        <p>
            At the University of Greenwich, the cost of studying students is only 1/10 compared to studying in the UK to get a Bachelor's degree from the University of Greenwich UK.
        </p>
